window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>Elemental Empire: The Complete Series </i></b><b>contains all five books in the epic H-Lit fantasy series by Peter North.</b></p> <p>When Logan Greenwood is transported to another world, he thinks he's died and gone to heaven. Beautiful elves, nymphs, and other magical beings are drawn to him, and he feels the stirrings of a mysterious power within himself as well.</p> <p>It should be a dream come true. But Logan's dream becomes a nightmare when he realizes that the enchanting realm is on the brink of war and that he's the only one who can save it from destruction.</p>"; 
